160
00:06:36,040 --> 00:06:38,000
Abide in peace。

161
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,760
Abide in peace。

162
00:06:39,760 --> 00:06:40,760
Abide in peace。

163
00:06:40,760 --> 00:06:41,760
すごい。

