182
00:07:09,200 --> 00:07:10,200
ええ。

183
00:07:10,200 --> 00:07:12,160
With this ring, I thee wed。

184
00:07:12,160 --> 00:07:14,480
With this ring, I thee wed。

185
00:07:14,480 --> 00:07:16,480
With this ring, I thee wed。

186
00:07:16,480 --> 00:07:17,480
なるほど。

187
00:07:17,480 --> 00:07:20,840
ここには古い英単語が二つ入っていますね。

188
00:07:20,840 --> 00:07:22,520
まず、thee。

189
00:07:22,520 --> 00:07:23,520
Thee。

190
00:07:23,520 --> 00:07:24,520
T-H-E-E。

191
00:07:24,520 --> 00:07:25,520
T-H-E-E。

192
00:07:25,520 --> 00:07:27,840
Thee。

193
00:07:27,840 --> 00:07:31,520
